I published the full story of the trade that lost me 31 dollars.

3
00:00:06,138 --> 00:00:07,569
I can't code.

4
00:00:07,569 --> 00:00:09,597
9 years in crypto.

5
00:00:09,597 --> 00:00:11,736
AI trades my thousand.

6
00:00:11,736 --> 00:00:13,152
Day 11.

7
00:00:13,152 --> 00:00:17,611
This was the trade that told me my 90% win rate was fiction.

8
00:00:17,611 --> 00:00:22,152
I wrote it down — all the numbers, the full timeline, no sweetening.

9
00:00:22,152 --> 00:00:26,375
I thought it would be the coldest piece of content I'd post all year.

10
00:00:26,375 --> 00:00:30,513
