11
00:00:30,513 --> 00:00:34,736
You know how much a losing trade is worth if you're willing to write it down?

12
00:00:34,736 --> 00:00:38,386
More than ten winning ones you never bothered to.

13
00:00:38,386 --> 00:00:40,777
Losing stories teach people.

14
00:00:40,777 --> 00:00:43,402
Winning stories just entertain.

15
00:00:43,402 --> 00:00:48,513
Day 12 tomorrow — I rebuilt every agent I'd put on a schedule.

16
00:00:48,513 --> 00:00:49,875
Follow along.

